Package com.intellij.psi

Interface PsiKeyword

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iconable, PsiElement, PsiJavaToken, UserDataHolder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LightKeyword, PsiKeywordImpl

    public interface PsiKeyword
extends PsiJavaToken
    Represents a Java keyword. Constants defined in this interface represent all keywords and literals of the Java language.
